comment:
Hi My name is Michelle.  Thank you for doing this video, I am so happy that you are addressing this issue specifically.  If you don't want to read it all, it's ok.  This is just my opinion only.  
It's starts with her & the divorce settlement agreement, signed by both. JD's 7 Mill Dollars!  Does AHT know that when you sign a legal document in the United States, CA or VA, that you are swearing to the court that what you are writing and signing are TRUE and CORRECT to the best of her ability?  I can't imagine what excuse she comes up with regarding that.  Does she also know that the court can charge her with contempt & perjury for not donating the money as she promised and committed, not pledge Over a 10yr time frame??? WHAT, she used DONATED, as in past tense, she did this in a video, new articles, everything.  Meaning no direct to her, but did she skip English class too  AHT likes to play the fool but she isn't, she is very smart, maybe a little too smart for her own good, & She thinks we are all clueless, she has her small fan base sticking up for her.  So Yes, bullying or threats of any kind should not be tolerated no matter who she is.  If her small fan base would take the time to read the evidence, maybe they will see it too.  You can't just go off words, being a public figure who refuses to actually look at evidence in fact. IDK.  
The late great Jerry Judge knew it,  he told JD's sister, in Australia what AHT did and what JD needs at that time.  It would be amazing if he were here.
The UK trial also took a lot out of us, it did to me, just because I am sure you will agree, we were hoping JD would win an appeal or even a retrial.  I remember so long ago, thinking that she broke the divorce settlement, it's starts here, before the WP op ed.  IMHO She should have to pay him $14million?, for spending JD's money and not doing the promised donations, she lied so much and got greedy, she should have the pay the same amount that she demanded from him for not sending the money directly to her, after he made the first payments to the charity's & that JD will file contempt against her, (hopefully), which to me is amazing news, she lied about the donations, now its time to face the music.  
The trial is a little over a year from now.  So much time for more info to be released to the public regarding JD innocence & the more truth coming out that AHT lied and these are not little lies, there are huge and should be taken very seriously.   
IMHO  I was thinking about this so much during the UK Trial, that what if, just what if Justice happens there.  I was half on and off basically like if he gets it, it will be monumental to all the Men who suffer at the hands of a women committing emotional and physical abuse on them & then switching abuse around to show it was the man.  Just like the movie Gone Girl, Its rare to see this type of justice, because the status quo is women are victims, not men.  
I apologize for length, I tend to get on a soapbox, with this case.  I also am passionate about someone, JD, getting smeared in such a despicable way by her and little team, attempting to ruin HIS LIFE & WORK having false allegations planted in People Mag by AH & other major platforms WP, the Me-too movement. 
I saw the recent article in People Mag, that her lies are caught ( which was proven in the UK Trial) & JD is filing documents that she broke the divorce degree.  (Crossing Fingers) 
I would never wish ill on anyone, however the irony of that (interesting to see the switch up from People MAG), & AH defaming JD, manipulating, and attempting to spin the narrative to her being a victim, lying to the public with more lies and deceit, attempted extortion, committing perjury, her list is way to long for me to list them all, but the worst ones, are that during one of her assaults' on him, JD almost lost his finger, caught MERSA 3 times, because she was drunk, high, & taking prescription medication.  Here is a really good question?  How is a doctor supposed to treat a patient when they are willing to compromise themselves by consuming the list of medications plus wine.  I would be curious to know if that issue will addressed in the VA court.  I was wondering how she can get these prescriptions, than abuse them.  Hopefully this case will bring that to light, so she can get the help she needs.
 I will admit that at first, I was surprised & sad about what was happening to JD.  I had a hard time accepting it in the beginning, what is mindboggling is how quickly a lie can spread like wild fire and destroy everything in it's/her path & ruin a person.  IMHO: That is what AHT is trying to do to JD.
I agree to not give her any relevance online anymore by name, I have been posting mostly about how a miscarriage's of Justice has taken place and it's not over here, because like you were saying, that is what she wants.  She wants to get reactions & information on our IP address's, location, & life, just for having an opinion based on facts presented in a case against her.  (SCARY)
To me, IMHO I honestly think that her mindset right now may be, your playing with fire!!  The more media that prints or says her name, is just filling her head with more nonsense, that she matters in the same way JD does.  She will never get that recognition, NOPE, I know you agree with me on this, but your right, posting more positive about Johnny Depp.
She does not care if her PR is good or bad.  All she cares about is her name being in the press so she can try to win more sympathy to her ongoing lies & I honestly can't wait for the VA trial.  This is THE UNITED STATES OF AMERICA, we don't play around with our court system here.  No alleged payouts, No alleged relationship directly with the Judges, bribes from millionaire friend, or paying out family and friends to lie & commit perjury, anyone Directly involved in the trial.
To her, this is all JD's fault, she did this to herself and now she has to face the truth.  Two things may happen, she snaps, & the end result is the worst case scenario, which I would never want someone to be in that place. With extreme mood swings, she is in a place almost like ok let's fight with fan's on twitter.  I was like Wait What?  This is a very scary situation, when you are dealing with a proven liar, there is no telling what may happen, or what lengths she will go through to protect her wallet.  She doesn't wait to react, she just does no caring what the outcome will be.  Which we all know she has told al lot of BS, but she is in too deep now she won't do an about face.  Wow, she is very deluded, detached to the reality that is right before her.  I tweeted last week, outside of sharing public articles, court doc's, & anyone just wanting to professional discussion, what may be the biggest case of DV on a celebrity's scale, of our time.
Even more so, that JD is completely innocent of everything she has falsely alleged.  She is attempting to frame him, & take his money, like $100million, this is truth.  She is calculated, conniving, and the truth is coming out, for someone who is a control freak like AHT, I can't imagine her nerves right now.  if It weren't for the Tabloids, her lies wouldn't have been exposed, so for that, her attempt to extort JD, her secret recordings, her truth every witness except for like 3 people (her people), they know who she really is.  IMHO  I wouldn't want my daughter watching her in any Disney Movies or anything for children, she is a horrible person.  She never sent over all the tapes he asked her for.  She admits on tape she hasn't turned them I have no idea why Disney is keeping her, what they did to JD is unforgivable.  Sorry this was long, I know there is alot going on with this case, let's hope it goes good for Johnny Depp  #JusticeforJohnnyDepp
